message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper discusses a Question Answering (QA) system based on contextual word embeddings and fine-tuned for biomedical question answering tasks. This falls under the domain of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning (ML), which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS such as Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
